<HEADLINE>

<s docid="FT943-15291" num="4"> FT 09 JUL 94 / 139 clergy resign</s>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<s docid="FT943-15291" num="5"> A total of 139 Church of England clergymen have resigned over the ordination of women priests.</s>

<s docid="FT943-15291" num="6"> The Church Commissioners told the Church's general synod in York that resignations were likely to cost Pounds 3.2m by the end of next year in claims for resettlement payments, housing subsidies and other grants.</s>
