<s docid="FT924-4560" num="4"> FT 02 DEC 92 / World News In Brief: Gummer quits Synod</s>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<s docid="FT924-4560" num="5"> Agriculture minister John Gummer resigned from the General Synod of the Church of England in protest at its decision to allow the ordination of women priests.</s>
</TEXT>
